 </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Whoop I didn't say but I start IAO<br>
<br>
This is a very solid and flexible deck. It can shut down opponents drains with Decree and fliped ISB. Enough space to go probing and solid on the ground.<br>
<br>
The characters are mainly ISB's with piloting skills. Igar is good behind 3 of the walkers, Vader is strong and Arnet is the pilot of Tempest Scout 1 and is death to Arconas<br>
<br>
The Ice Storms help clean out Hoth unless their playing with something like Speeder ops (trouble!)<br>
<br>
Strong against most ground decks, enough space to find the HB and easy to play. </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech SW: CCG <BR> Play With Power <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
